cells: Hello all and welcome to my blindfolded information sheet.
Here you will find all of the algorithms I use, including the following sets:
Some alg sets that are missing that I plan to include at a later date are as follows:
If you have any recommended algorithms for me, right click and leave a comment in the relevant place!
If you would like to contribute to a set that I have not started, please contact me.
Please note that I would not recommend copying my images, however to use as inspiration only.
Do not leave comments on the images sheet, they are personal and your suggestion might be a very weak image for me.
There are plenty of images I have that pertain to me that will either mean nothing or be a weak image for you.
This sheet is currently undergoing a significant amount of changes and upgrades.
Feel free to use the algorithms available but it is being constantly updated at the moment.
If you have any suggestions or questions feel free to message me on Facebook or contact me on Discord (Mollerz#0781).
FYI I will not accept you as a friend on Facebook unless we've interacted at a competition so just direct message.
